        | My name is Nick. I'm currently a software developer at <a href="http://www.artefactgroup.com/content/person/nick-alto/"> Artefact </a>. I grew up in the Pacific Northwest in rainy Portland, OR and have since moved to the even grayer skies of Seattle, WA. In my opinion the best video game of all time is the Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time and the best console of all time was the Super Nintendo. If I’m not heads down working on a <a href="https://github.com/nickalto/starterpack.js" >side project in Node.js</a>, iOS or Ruby I’m typically scribbling on a canvas.
